00:27:43.520 --> 00:27:47.350
Two faces on top, two faces
twisted 90 degrees, and

00:27:47.350 --> 00:27:48.110
inverted down.

00:27:48.110 --> 00:27:50.006
AUDIENCE: So that means
an 8 bar would be a

00:27:50.006 --> 00:27:50.954
