degrees and inverted down.

00:28:16.920 --> 00:28:19.760
But you can assemble those
at this same point.

00:28:19.760 --> 00:28:23.710
So you would have eight
translations 45 degrees apart.

00:28:23.710 --> 00:28:25.240
And that's impossible
in a lattice.

